Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}就像宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}一般的存在
