Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你要不要也来这里发掘宝藏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs23}今夏 最感人大作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs23}在此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs23}终将揭开帏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要搬走的是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 放开我
